lead_paragraph: Connor Jaeger and Abbey Weitzeil wrapped up eight days of cut-throat competition by claiming the last two wins at the U.S. Olympic trials on Sunday as the final pieces of the Rio Games swim team were put in place.

headline.print_headline: Final Pieces in Place, U.S. Ready for Rio Plunge
